Elena Ugomma, second child of comedian Bovi, has revealed her father was in a marital relationship with another woman. She revealed the secret in a show with singer Poco Lee and her father. The trio was having a nice “yo mama’ joke time, a popular battle of words session between people who try to jokingly ‘roast’ their mothers. Elena started the joke session assisted by Poco Lee when she said ” yo mama is so dumb that when she opens a blank book, she wasn’t able to read it.”   Yemi Alade groans over butt-induced inconvenience     MI Abaga seeks financial support for ailing Eedris Abdul…     Moving abroad changed my life – Wakawaka Doctor   Bovi replied: “Yo mama is ugly she had to depend on me for your beauty.” In retaliation, Elena said: “Come here!, since it’s your wife you are insulting, let’s go to your other wife that you broke up with because….” In order not to spill more secrets, the comedian put a hand on his daughter’s mouth and prevented her from speaking further. This disclosure created a whet appetite among netizens who asked bloggers to dig into the story and reveal what the child was prevented from spilling.